        <abstract> 
<p>CD sends thanks to Mr Noel for allowing him to see article [sent by Alice Bonham-Carter, see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">4722</hi>]. CD is pleased at Bernhard von Cotta’s remarks on species; very few of the older distinguished geologists have so favourable a view of his work. He was particularly pleased to read Cotta’s remarks on the azoic formations.</p> 
        </abstract>
